---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import 'aos/dist/aos.css';
---

<Layout title='WebWanniassa'>
  <main class='prose w-[100vw] bg-white'>
    <div class="navbar bg-base-100 w-[100vw]">
      <div class="navbar-start">
        <div class="dropdown">
          <div tabindex="0" role="button" class="btn btn-ghost lg:hidden">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-5 w-5"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor">
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M4 6h16M4 12h8m-8 6h16" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <ul
            tabindex="0"
            class="menu menu-sm dropdown-content bg-base-100 rounded-box z-[1] mt-3 w-52 p-2 shadow">
            <li><a>Contact</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost text-xl no-underline text-secondary">Web Wanniassa</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero w-[100vw] min-h-screen">
      <div class="hero-content flex-col lg:flex-row">
        <div class="mr-10" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="500">
          <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">Canberra's Leading Website Design Agency</h1>
          <p class="text-2xl">
            Get a custom designed, high-speed, responsive website with a modern design that <b>actually</b> helps your business' bottom line
          </p>
        </div>
        <form class="max-w-lg m-5 bg-gray-100 p-10 rounded-lg" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="500" action="https://api.web3forms.com/submit" method="POST">
          <h1>Get Your Free Quote Today</h1>
          <input type="hidden" name="access_key" value="2c81c047-2e38-410e-b70e-6644293a0009">
          <label class="input input-bordered flex items-center gap-2 mt-5">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              viewBox="0 0 16 16"
              fill="currentColor"
              class="h-4 w-4 opacity-70">
              <path
                d="M8 8a3 3 0 1 0 0-6 3 3 0 0 0 0 6ZM12.735 14c.618 0 1.093-.561.872-1.139a6.002 6.002 0 0 0-11.215 0c-.22.578.254 1.139.872 1.139h9.47Z" />
            </svg>
            <input type="text" class="grow" placeholder="Your Name" name="name"/>
          </label>
          <label class="input input-bordered flex items-center gap-2 mt-5">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              viewBox="0 0 16 16"
              fill="currentColor"
              class="h-4 w-4 opacity-70">
              <path
                d="M2.5 3A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1 4.5v.793c.026.009.051.02.076.032L7.674 8.51c.206.1.446.1.652 0l6.598-3.185A.755.755 0 0 1 15 5.293V4.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 13.5 3h-11Z" />
              <path
                d="M15 6.954 8.978 9.86a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-1.956 0L1 6.954V11.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 2.5 13h11a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.5-1.5V6.954Z" />
            </svg>
            <input type='email' class="grow" placeholder="Email" name="email"/>
          </label>
          <textarea class="textarea textarea-bordered min-w-96 mt-5" placeholder="Your Message" name="message"></textarea>
          <button class="btn btn-secondary mt-5">Send</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero w-[100vw] min-h-[40vh] my-24">
      <div class="hero-content text-center">
        <div class="max-w-lg" >
          <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-secondary" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">About Us</h1>
          <p data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
            Web Wanniassa is focused to helping small businesses in the Canberra region. We provide an emphasis on a website having a goal, a meaning for existing.
            This means that every website that you see from us helps you convert potential customers into paying patrons.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 justify-center place-items-center content-center w-[100vw] lg:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="card bg-base-100 w-96 shadow-xl" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title">Easy To Work With</h2>
          <p>Wanniassa Web took the stress out of building our website. They listened to what we wanted and delivered a site that looks great and is easy for us to update.</p>
          <div class="card-actions justify-end">
            <p>- Alex Jackson <i class="fa-solid fa-star text-secondary ml-2"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star text-secondary"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star text-secondary"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star text-secondary"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star text-secondary"></i></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card bg-base-100 w-96 shadow-xl" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title">Great Value</h2>
          <p>We got a professional website without breaking the bank. Wanniassa Web offered a competitive price and were upfront about all the costs involved.</p>
          <div class="card-actions justify-end">
            <p>- Chris Smith <i class="fa-solid fa-star text-secondary ml-2"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star text-secondary"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star text-secondary"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star text-secondary"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star text-secondary"></i></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card bg-base-100 w-96 shadow-xl" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title">Responsive and Helpful</h2>
          <p>Whenever we had a question or needed help, Wanniassa Web was always quick to respond. They made sure we were happy with every step of the process.</p>
          <div class="card-actions justify-end">
            <p>- Jamie O'Connor Cox <i class="fa-solid fa-star text-secondary ml-2"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star text-secondary"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star text-secondary"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star text-secondary"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star text-secondary"></i></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <footer class="footer w-[100vw] mt-64 border-t-2 text-neutral-content items-center px-4 py-2 ">
      <aside class="grid-flow-col items-center align-middle">
        <a class="btn btn-ghost no-underline text-xl align-top">Web Wanniassa</a>
        <p>Copyright Â© {new Date().getFullYear()} - All right reserved</p>
      </aside>
    </footer>
    <script>
      import * as AOS from 'aos';
      AOS.init();
    </script>
  </main>
</Layout>
